    <item>
      <title>民意调查显示法国勒庞将赢得首轮总统选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/france-s-le-pen-would-win-first-round-president-vote-poll-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[投票结束后进行的一项民意调查显示，尽管玛丽娜·勒庞所领导的极右翼政党国民联盟在周日的立法选举中跌至第三位，但她将在 2027 年法国下一届总统选举的第一轮选举中领先。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/france-s-le-pen-would-win-first-round-president-vote-poll-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 10:47:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
